dc_description_s: This data layer represents roads for Rock County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, 'Rock_Roads_2018.gdb'. [This feature class contains all of the roads in Rock County, Wisconsin. They are captured as needed using GPS. The main purpose of this data is for use by 9-1-1 Communications as input into the Computer Aided Dispatch system. They do, however, fit many other purposes as used by other county departments.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.
